<div class="privacy-main">
    <div class="privacy-hero">
        <div class="privacy-badge">Legal · Privacy</div>
        <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="privacy-updated">
            This demo website is a training project for a Pharmacy Delivery System (Pharmacy Marts).
            It is not a real production system and is used only for learning and educational purposes.
        </p>
